* '''[[Football League Cup]]'''
**'''''(4):'' [[1965 Football League Cup Final|1964–65]], [[1998 Football League Cup Final|1997–98]], [[2005 Football League Cup Final|2004–05]], [[2007 Football League Cup Final|2006–07]]'''
